PrecisGranting to the DEPARTMENT OF THE ENVIRONMENT, for a term of up to fifty (50) years, of a circular-shaped easement around a proposed automatic weather station to be installed on St. Quentin Island, in the City of Trois-Rivieres, Quebec, in order to prohibit the installation of any obstructions within a 100 metre radius of its facility.
